data: {"messageId":"WCyb84iDqTdCaJRectg2Z","role":"assistant","content":"---\n\n## Results — All Three Operations Failed\n\nEvery Kubernetes tool call returns the identical error. Here is the full report:\n\n| Step | Operation | Tool | Status | Error |\n|:----:|-----------|------|:------:|-------|\n| 1 | **Get events** | `k8s_get_events` | ❌ | `Invalid kube-config file. No configuration found.` |\n| 2 | **Check if pod exists** | `k8s_list_pods` | ❌ | `Invalid kube-config file. No configuration found.` |\n| 3 | **Retry pod creation** | `k8s_apply_yaml` | ❌ | `Invalid kube-config file. No configuration found.` |\n\n---\n\n## What Went Wrong\n\nThe failure is **not** with the pod spec or the `agentic-dev` namespace — the problem is upstream of all Kubernetes operations:\n\n> **Error:** `Kubernetes client initialization failed: Invalid kube-config file. No configuration found.`\n\nThe **K8s MCP server has no kubeconfig loaded**. Without it, the client library cannot authenticate to the Kubernetes API server, so every `k8s_*` tool — apply, list, get, events — fails at the connection stage before any cluster request is made.\n\n**The pod was never created.** The request never reached the Kubernetes API server.\n\n---\n\n## Root Cause\n\nThis is a **known recurring issue** (5th occurrence across our conversations). The MCP proxy pod stores its kubeconfig ephemerally. When the pod restarts or gets rescheduled, the credential is lost and all Kubernetes tooling goes blind.\n\n## Required Fix (from a host with direct cluster access)\n\n```bash\n# 1. Check the MCP proxy pod status\nkubectl get pods -n openagentic -l app=openagentic-mcp-proxy\n\n# 2. Collect crash logs before restart\nkubectl logs -n openagentic -l app=openagentic-mcp-proxy --previous\n\n# 3. Re-inject AKS credentials\naz aks get-credentials --resource-group <RG> --name <CLUSTER> --overwrite-existing\n\n# 4. Restart the proxy to pick up the new kubeconfig\nkubectl rollout restart deployment/openagentic-mcp-proxy -n openagentic\n```\n\nOnce the kubeconfig is restored, I can immediately re-run all three steps. Let me know when credentials have been re-provisioned.","timestamp":"2026-02-21T00:26:43.579Z","mcpCalls":[{"id":"toolu_bdrk_018kdrLVm5NS1FXKtACMzosN","name":"k8s_get_events","tool":"k8s_get_events","toolName":"k8s_get_events","serverId":"openagentic_kubernetes","serverName":"openagentic_kubernetes","executedOn":"mcp-proxy","arguments":{"namespace":"agentic-dev"},"result":{"content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"error\": \"Kubernetes client initialization failed: Invalid kube-config file. No configuration found.\"\n}"}],"structuredContent":{"result":{"success":false,"error":"Kubernetes client initialization failed: Invalid kube-config file. No configuration found."}},"isError":false},"status":"completed","startTime":1771633585467,"endTime":1771633586686,"duration":1219,"timestamp":"2026-02-21T00:26:26.686Z"},{"id":"toolu_bdrk_01HVJ1c4BMFJy3mtBmAZ3r57","name":"k8s_list_pods","tool":"k8s_list_pods","toolName":"k8s_list_pods","serverId":"openagentic_kubernetes","serverName":"openagentic_kubernetes","executedOn":"mcp-proxy","arguments":{"namespace":"agentic-dev","label_selector":"test=val-02"},"result":{"content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"error\": \"Kubernetes client initialization failed: Invalid kube-config file. No configuration found.\"\n}"}],"structuredContent":{"result":{"success":false,"error":"Kubernetes client initialization failed: Invalid kube-config file. No configuration found."}},"isError":false},"status":"completed","startTime":1771633585467,"endTime":1771633586686,"duration":1219,"timestamp":"2026-02-21T00:26:26.686Z"},{"id":"toolu_bdrk_01A2MvLA9USc6m2bSf6aVZ7k","name":"k8s_apply_yaml","tool":"k8s_apply_yaml","toolName":"k8s_apply_yaml","serverId":"openagentic_kubernetes","serverName":"openagentic_kubernetes","executedOn":"mcp-proxy","arguments":{"yaml_content":"apiVersion: v1\nkind: Pod\nmetadata:\n  name: val-test-nginx\n  namespace: agentic-dev\n  labels:\n    app: val-test\n    test: val-02\nspec:\n  containers:\n  - name: nginx\n    image: nginx:alpine\n    ports:\n    - containerPort: 80\n    resources:\n      limits:\n        memory: 64Mi\n        cpu: 100m","namespace":"agentic-dev"},"result":{"content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"error\": \"Kubernetes client initialization failed: Invalid kube-config file. No configuration found.\"\n}"}],"structuredContent":{"result":{"success":false,"error":"Kubernetes client initialization failed: Invalid kube-config file. No configuration found."}},"isError":false},"status":"completed","startTime":1771633590059,"endTime":1771633590500,"duration":441,"timestamp":"2026-02-21T00:26:30.500Z"}],"tokenUsage":{"prompt_tokens":0,"completion_tokens":579,"total_tokens":579},"model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","source":"database","confirmed":true,"final":true}

